From ages 14 to 24, nearly 70–80% of people experience acne—and it can occur in any season. Excess scrubbing, home remedies, or quick fixes won’t cure it… they can actually make things worse.

The real concern? Acne scars and open pores, which are much harder to treat later. Early and proper treatment with a dermatologist is key to preventing long-term damage.

✨ Don’t wait. Treat acne the right way, at the right time.

